com.here.platform.location.core.geospatial.javadsl

Interface GeoCoordinateHolder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoCoordinate, GeoCoordinateLocation

    public interface GeoCoordinateHolder
    Represents objects containing geocoordinates.

    When using types that implement this interface, other parts of the API will work out-of-the-box. If a type doesn't implement it, a GeoCoordinateAdapter might need to be provided instead.
